\pard\tx1440\tx2880\tx4320\tx5760\qj\fi0\sb80\sa0\li0\ri0\f0\fs24\b0\i0\ul0\strike0\scaps0\cf0 2. Set the proportionality rato of the `\b 2\b0 ' signature of the third staff to 18/8.\par
\pard\tx1440\tx2880\tx4320\tx5760\qj\fi0\sb80\sa0\li0\ri0\f0\fs24\b0\i0\ul0\strike0\scaps0\cf0 3. Set the proportionality rato of the `\b 3\b0 ' signature of the fourth staff to 18/12.\par
\pard\tx1440\tx2880\tx4320\tx5760\qj\fi0\sb80\sa0\li0\ri0\f0\fs24\b0\i0\ul0\strike0\scaps0\cf0 4. Set the Adjustment Option in the System Inspector so that barlines are not forced to coincide, as shown here:\par
\pard\tx1440\tx2880\tx4320\tx5760\qc\fi0\sb80\sa0\li0\ri0\f0\fs24\b0\i0\ul0\strike0\scaps0\cf0 {{\NeXTGraphic4 graphic_3.tiff \width3840\height1940
